Windows environment:
Install msys and mingw https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/
Install glut32 http://www.xmission.com/~nate/glut.html
Install ftgl https://sourceforge.net/projects/ftgl/develop
Install freetype2 http://www.freetype.org/index2.html
Install zlib http://www.zlib.net/
Install openalsoft http://kcat.strangesoft.net/openal.html#download
Install freealut and openal http://connect.creativelabs.com/openal/Downloads/Forms/AllItems.aspx
Install libogg and libvorbis http://xiph.org/downloads/
Install boost http://www.boost.org/

Set enviroment variables before starts eclipse: 

LIBRARY_PATH = dll dirs

CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH = include dirs 

PATH = %LIBRARY_PATH%